title: Dreft | Amazinghood: Please Be Pudding
description:
Mommyhood throws you major curveballs – especially when your newly crawling baby does a little exploring. Dreft Stage 2: Active Baby detergent helps moms remove 99% of baby food stains and all of the messes baby finds while crawling in grass and dirt.

With Dreft Laundry Detergent’s family of products for every stage of babyhood, you’re covered every step of the way along the big, messy, beautiful journey of Amazinghood.
